    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "That's a good start. Can you expand on the \"natural rights\" part? Specifically, how would a philosopher like Locke or Nozick argue that any state-mandated content moderation or algorithm regulation is an overstep of the social contract?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
